	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=111670><span id=Sage>Vorish</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>308 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Requires a toolbox (8 or 10 slot), Mana Battery - Class Six (storebought or looted).&nbsp;&nbsp;To recharge, put the two items in the toolbox and click combine.  Requires no skill and does not require that you be a gnome.<br><br>Sold by Maryalis N'Ryt at neg 850 pos 200 in PoK (evil/south side of PoK, easternmost building between the Neriak and Ogguk portal stones, inside through the door on the left).  <br><br>Price was 106pp with 100 CHA.  This means that the per-use cost is only ~5pp vs ~15pp for a shrink potion.  I paid 700pp for my device, which means that after only 70 uses, I'll have paid it off.<br><br>(As mentioned in this thread: <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=16414&amp;mid=104361072612178" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=16414&amp;mid=104361072612178</a>)<br><br>All tinkered items can be recharged in this manner (different items require different batteries).<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Apr 21 11:50:09 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
